l this help me come up with ideas of what I should write about, it will also make sure that my content is specifically useful to you.</p><p>So, if you want to know how to best use WordPress&#8217;s built in http class to integrate with an existing API, how to add your own taxonomies to your site, how to make your theme more extensible, or almost anything else WordPress related, please just ask!</p><p><div\nclass=\'gform_wrapper\' id=\'gform_wrapper_3\' ><form\nmethod=\'post\' enctype=\'multipart/form-data\'  id=\'gform_3\' class=\'\' action=\'\'><div\nclass=\'gform_heading\'><h3 class=\'gform_title\'>WordPress Question</h3> <span\nclass=\'gform_description\'>Ask me your WordPress question!</span></div><div\nclass=\'gform_body\'><ul\nid=\'gform_fields_3\' class=\'gform_fields top_label\'><li\nid=\'field_3_1\' class=\'gfield\' ><label\nclass=\'gfield_label\' for=\'input_3_1.3\'>Your Name<span\nclass=\'gfield_required\'>*</span></label><div\nclass=\'ginput_complex ginput_container\' id=\'input_3_1\'><span\nid=\'input_3_1_3_container\' class=\'ginput_left\'><input\ntype=\'text\' name=\'input_1.3\' id=\'input_3_1.3\' value=\'\' tabindex=\'1\' /><label\nfor=\'input_3_1.3\'>First</label></span><span\nid=\'input_3_1_6_container\' class=\'ginput_right\'><input\ntype=\'text\' name=\'input_1.6\' id=\'input_3_1.6\' value=\'\' tabindex=\'2\' /><label\nfor=\'input_3_1.6\'>Last</label></span></div></li><li\nid=\'field_3_2\' class=\'gfield\' ><label\nclass=\'gfield_label\' for=\'input_3_2\'>E-Mail Address<span\nclass=\'gfield_required\'>*</span></label><div\nclass=\'ginput_container\'><input\nname=\'input_2\' id=\'input_3_2\' type=\'text\' value=\'\' class=\'medium\'  tabindex=\'3\'  /></div></li><li\nid=\'field_3_3\' class=\'gfield\' ><label\nclass=\'gfield_label\' for=\'input_3_3\'>Your WordPress Question<span\nclass=\'gfield_required\'>*</span></label><div\nclass=\'ginput_container\'><input\nname=\'input_3\' id=\'input_3_3\' type=\'text\' value=\'\' class=\'medium\'  tabindex=\'