INSERT INTO `wp090901_posts` VALUES (342, 2, '2009-06-10 11:00:00', '2009-06-10 09:00:00', 'Religion is a fascinating phenomenon to me. A few people in my life have tried their best to find purpose through it, with varying succes. This search for a purpose puzzles me. Cults, Eastern teachings, Western religions, New Age nonsense … it\'s quite the list. But I left ‘faith’ behind me around the time I stopped believing in Santa and the Easter Bunny.  I get more satisfaction from logic and discussion. Also, I\'ve never been much of a group person, so the mandatory meeting of people every Friday, Saturday or Sunday is out of the question anyway.\r\n\r\nI\'m reading ‘The God Delusion‘, by Richard Dawkins and enjoying it very much. I\'d recommend it to anyone interested in religion. And if you\'re not much of a reader, there\'s always <a target="_blank" href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9WQ0i3nCx60&feature=PlayList&p=B1C425D6FDC2E0C0&index=9">Christopher Hitchins\' piece about Mother Theresa</a> on YouTube. If you like your holy houses steamrolled.\r\n\r\n<strong>Edit:</strong>\r\nI\'ve made a topic <a target="_blank" href="http://forums.tnppress.com/viewtopic.php?f=13&t=214&start=0">in the forums</a> if anyone wants to share his views.', '059 - Religious awakenings', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '059-religious-awakenings', '', '', '2009-11-19 14:11:28', '2009-11-19 14:11:28', '', 0, 'http://www.mindbase21.be/comics/2009/06/10/059-religious-awakenings/', 0, 'webcomic_post', '', 3); 
INSERT INTO `wp090901_posts` VALUES (348, 2, '2009-06-17 11:45:00', '2009-06-17 09:45:00', 'Tattoos have a reputation of being tags for all kinds of bad people, ranging from pirates to gangs. But they\'re also art or even ways to show devotion, in other cultures.\r\nI\'m in the market for getting a good tattoo, but being in a constant state of confusion, I\'m worried about the result. I want something that I can still look at 10 years from now and go “awesome!”.\r\nFreaky coincidence, but this story made headlines today:<a target="_blank" href="http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/worldnews/article-1193384/Teen-suing-tattoo-artist-8-500-asked-stars-face--ended-56.html"> Girl asked for 3 stars and got 56 on her face</a>.\r\nI\'d like to open up the floor to your experiences with getting a tattoo. Got any pictures or opinions on them? Feel free to share.\r\nLeave it in the comments, or even better,<a href="http://forums.tnppress.com/viewtopic.php?f=34&t=224" target="_blank"> check out the forum</a>.\r\n\r\nIn other news, fellow TNP artist Evan Diaz rebooted his webcomic last Monday. Adjust your Musings-bookmark and welcome <a href="http://pajamaforest.com/" target="_blank">Pajama Forest</a>!', '060 - Inked up', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '060-inked-up', '', '', '2009-11-19 14:12:05', '2009-11-19 14:12:05', '', 0, 'http://www.mindbase21.be/comics/2009/06/17/060-inked-up/', 0, 'webcomic_post', '', 3); 
INSERT INTO `wp090901_posts` VALUES (355, 2, '2009-06-24 16:00:00', '2009-06-24 14:00:00', 'It’s my destiny to be an angry old bastard when I\'m 70 or 80 years old. And I’ll enjoy it to the fullest!\r\n\r\nOn Sunday I launched my brandnew <a href="store.tnppress.com/mci-shop/" target="_blank">shop</a> over at TNP Press. The first product is an awesome button pack featuring artwork from the comic. And because I know you’re all cheap bastards,<strong> I’m giving some away for free!</strong> The first 5 people* in the comments or replying to me on <a href="http://www.twitter.com/mindbase21" target="_blank">twitter</a> get a pack. Ready? Set… Go!\r\n\r\n<small>* excluding spambots, dead presidents<del datetime="2009-06-24T14:33:19+00:00"> and fellow TNP members</del>, including TNP members</small>', '061 - Angry old man 01', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '061-angry-old-man-01', '', '', '2010-07-21 10:51:48', '2010-07-21 08:51:48', '', 0, 'http://www.mindbase21.be/comics/2009/06/24/061-angry-old-man-01/', 0, 'webcomic_post', '', 2); 
INSERT INTO `wp090901_posts` VALUES (365, 2, '2009-07-01 16:00:00', '2009-07-01 14:00:00', 'It’s never quite like in the movies, is it? Although I’m glad not to have been set on fire, I am a little disappointed by the way my termination was handled last Thursday. Not even a small riot or a shout. Oh well.\r\nWhat are your experiences with being canned? Did you burn a couple of bridges on the way out or are you still pals with your old bosses? Are you seething with rage over ‘The state of the economy’ being used as a cover-up for mismanagement? Leave your remarks in the comments below, or take it to <a target="_blank" href="forums.tnppress.com/">the forum</a>.', '062 - Fired', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '062-fired', '', '', '2009-11-19 14:12:53', '2009-11-19 14:12:53', '', 0, 'http://www.mindbase21.be/comics/2009/07/01/062-fired/', 0, 'webcomic_post', '', 2); 
INSERT INTO `wp090901_posts` VALUES (368, 2, '2009-07-08 16:00:00', '2009-07-08 14:00:00', 'Get with the times, old man. Bears are people too.', '063 - Angry old man 02', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'angry-old-man-02', '', '', '2010-07-21 10:53:52', '2010-07-21 08:53:52', '', 0, 'http://www.mindbase21.be/comics/2009/07/08/angry-old-man-02/', 0, 'webcomic_post', '', 2); 
INSERT INTO `wp090901_posts` VALUES (369, 2, '2009-07-15 16:00:00', '2009-07-15 14:00:00', 'This one is a bit late because I forgot to upload it before going to work. But here it is now. And don\'t forget, kids: be responsible when picking a movie.\r\n\r\nAlso, there\'s still buttons available in the store. <a href="store.tnppress.com/mci-shop/" target="_blank">Take a peek.</a>', '064 - Crappy movies', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '064-crappy-movies', '', '', '2009-11-19 14:13:36', '2009-11-19 14:13:36', '', 0, 'http://www.mindbase21.be/comics/2009/07/15/064-crappy-movies/', 0, 'webcomic_post', '', 2); 
INSERT INTO `wp090901_posts` VALUES (380, 2, '2009-07-22 13:00:00', '2009-07-22 11:00:00', 'It’s vacation time again (hooray!), so you get some filler-art to tie you over for the week. Hope you like the knife-carrying dark elf. I don’t know what’s up with the goldfish.\r\nSee you all next week with a new Angry Old Man comic!', 'filler', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'filler-5', '', '', '2010-07-20 16:54:07', '2010-07-20 14:54:07', '', 0, 'http://www.mindbase21.be/comics/2009/07/22/filler-5/', 0, 'webcomic_post', '', 4); 
